Description: The Prova railing system from DOLLE offers interior and exterior railing systems that are component-based, easy to install, and beautifully designed. The Prova railing system offers several different configurations that provide a sleek, contemporary, custom look at DIY pricing. Prova railings are perfect for any home - creating dramatic sightlines outside, and making small spaces seem larger inside. Prova PA22b lag screws are constructed of zinc plated galvanized steel. PA22b lag screws are used to secure Prova aluminum top and side mount posts into a wood or composite backing. Requires a 5/16" pilot hole for installation. Prova top mount posts require 4 screws per post, side mount posts require 2 screws per post. No special skills required - Prova is designed for easy assembly with basic hand tools. Prova railings by DOLLE are the perfect railing system for today's modern, open floor plans inside while also providing beautiful, unobstructed sightlines outside!
Item Name: Dolle Prova PA22b Galvanized Steel Hex Screw Post Anchors (4-Piece)

Description: Wall art panels are made with a new generation of wood material, which reproduces a 350-year old structure of wood on a molecular level. We use our patented thermo-treatment technology to speed up the aging of the wood. If you compare the cell structure of 350-year old wood with the thermo-treated wood (see in the picture), you'll see that they are similar. So, we make a real 350-year old wood with our process, but it is a new product! Easy Planking wall art panels add character, warmth, and a rustic feel to any residential or commercial wall decor. In opposite to reclaimed lumber, which was staying outdoors for decades, our product is free of any insects and bacteria. Change the look of any room by adding the natural beauty of wood to your home or office decor. Easy Planking wall art panels are a real old-wood product, which creates a unique design solution for reclaimed lumber as wall decals or old-wood fashion interior styles. Use our wall art panels as a wall accent, picture frames, a substrate for collections of pictures, musical discs, photos, or any objects. Due to thermo-treatment of wood, use Easy Planking wall art panels even in bathrooms and in other high humidity areas.
Item Name: Easy Planking Thermo-Treated 1/2 in. x 16 in. x 16 in. Barn Wood Wall Decorative Panel / Picture Frame (4 Sq. Ft. per 2-Pack)

Description: Our beautiful panel moulding and corners add a decorative, historic, feel to walls, ceilings, and furniture pieces. The best part is you can make your own shapes and sizes by simply cutting the moulding piece down to size, and then butting them up to the decorative corners. Description: The Terrassotec Trilobular screw is used in the visible attachment of decking as wood-wood joints. It is only partially rust-resistant, not acid-resistant, relatively soft and not suitable for atmospheres containing chlorine. Advantages of Terrassotec Trilobular: Special screw geometry Drive thread ensures quick screwing Reinforced shank reduces risk of breaking or shearing off Under-head thread provides additional hold for deck boards. Trilobular base geometry Reduced screwing torque Reduced risk of screw breaking during screwing. 2-step head with under-head toothing Reduced splintering Reduced risk of timber splitting. Reinforced shank Suitable for many tropical woods Reduced risk of screw shearing off.

Description: Everbilt Lite Duty Steel U-Posts have tons of applications around the home and farm. Use to protect gardens from deer and other animals, create a temporary pasture, support young trees, or display warning signs. The U-Post measures 1-1/8 in. x 1-1/8 in. and has a total length of 4 ft. When the 3-1/2 in. anchor plate is totally buried in the ground, the post has an above ground height of 3 ft. The tightly welded plate also helps to minimize sideways or rotational movement of the post. These fence posts are made of 14-gauge steel for durability and are powder coated to protect from rust and weathering. The notched design makes it easy to secure fence to the post. No dig installation is made even easier by using the Everbilt Metal Fence Post Driver (Model 901147EB) to pound posts into the ground.
Item Name: Everbilt 1-1/8 in. x 1-1/8 in. x 4 ft. Green Steel Fence U Post with Anchor Plate
